<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Absurd" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Absúrd,</orth> (as for the accent, see <bibl default="NO">App. I, 1</bibl>) contrary to reason, insipid: <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 4, 137</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 2, 226</bibl>. <cit><quote>a fault to nature, to reason most a.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 2, 103</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>